[Student "S"]
{You are almost strong enough to bid the game right now, but you are worried about \Cs. If partner can Help out in that suit you'd be willing to try for 10 tricks. So you make a Help Suit Game Try of 3\C. Partner replies 3\H. What do you say next?  

When you ask partner to make a judgement call and he does so, you don't then override that call. You pass.}

